The paper focuses on the decision-making process of automated vehicles using deep reinforcement learning and simulation environments. This topic falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV).
